---

This software produces probabilistic earthquake *forecasts*, not deterministic
*predictions*. It is an independent research and education tool. It is NOT an
official earthquake early-warning or civil-protection system and must not be
used for life-safety decisions. For authoritative information, always defer to
your national seismological agency (in Chile, the Centro Sismológico Nacional,
CSN; and ONEMI/SENAPRED for civil protection).
